name: Hand drilled vintage cake stand
description:
Hand drilled cake stand made from genuine vintage plates. 
Optional tea cup can be added at an extra charge.

Two and 3 tier cake stands available with various different designs and choice of white, silver or gold centre fitting.
Each cake stand can be unscrewed for washing. **Hand wash only*


All of the plates are in excellent condition however as they are vintage please be aware some plates may have 'general wear and tear' marks. Please do not hesitate to email me with any questions you may have regarding this.
